message.body: Hey, I just saw that you called. What's up?
Hello. Not much just want to say hi and catch up. How have you been?

I'm really busy with work nowadays. I usually drop by Philadelphia to see my dad and do bank/city hall business before I need to get back to Baltimore. Otherwise, I'm okay!
How's your last year going? Job secured at PECO?
That's great man. Do you find your work more enjoyable now? You've been working there for a while.
No I haven't reach out yet. Although I should
